code: // @formatter:on /** * @param arg * @return * @see Java: Enum case insensitive Jersey Query Param Binding */ public static PublishableStatus fromString(String arg) { arg = "".concat(arg).toLowerCase(). if (!arg.isEmpty() && arg.startsWith("private")) { return private_. } if (!arg.isEmpty() && arg.startsWith("auto")) { return auto_draft. } return valueOf(arg). }
